metadata.name: Fallen Head 1
metadata.description:
The Fallen Heads are gods fallen from grace, literally. These Floating Head antagonists are cursed to float close to the earth, camouflaging themselves as their favourite Spirit and holding themselves up with whatever they have. Don't be fooled though, this group of vigilantes are powerful, armed and dangerous.

Check out the website Supernfty.com. Join the community on Discord - discord.gg/supernfty ; @SuperNfty On Twitter & Instagram.
